Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Teflon President on sticky ground
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xsbp
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Nov 1986
Sharp criticism from both sides as president comes clean about arms deal to Iran amid hostage negotiations. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less